                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>The quire marks are misplaced; the quiremarks from 7 (፯) to 13 (፲፫) are
                        written by a different hand.</note>
                     <note>Concerning the introduction, the contents and the postscript of the
                        Gospels, cp. R. ZUURMOND, Novum Testamentum Aethiopice: the Synoptic
                        Gospels, Part I: General Introduction, Part II: Edition of the Gospel of
                        Mark, Stuttgart 1989 (AeF 27), 1-31.</note>
                     <note>The content of the last leaf (<locus target="#12ra">12ra</locus> – rb
                        [l.6]) of the “Canon Tables” is summarizing the full text of the Canons
                        Table without columns.</note>
                  </msItem>
